plot: UPN's '96 fall promo features clips and interviews with the casts of sitcoms In the House, Malcolm & Eddie, Goode Behavior, Sparks, Homeboys in Outer Space and Moesha and Sci-Fi shows The Burning Zone, The Sentinel and Star Trek: Voyager.
